(1740, 1, '2018-03-25 22:03:32', '2018-03-25 22:03:32', '<div id=\"frontPageWelcome\">\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Welcome to the Comox Valley Potters Club</h1>\r\n<h3>We are a group of local potters who get together to create during studio time at the NIC Ceramics Studio. We also host club events, such as the YANA Chilli Bowl fundraiser, and various workshops. We have weekly access to an electric kiln and occasional access to raku and wood-burning kilns. We are always looking for new members.</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Please visit our <a href=\"http://localhost/membership/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">membership page</a> to download an application today.</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"frontPageBenefits\">\r\n<h4><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-2179\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/membership-300x300.png\" alt=\"Comox Valley Pottery Club Membership Icon\" width=\"350\" height=\"300\" /></h4>\r\n<h4>Access to the NIC ceramics studio every Wednesday from 830-5pm.</h4>\r\n<h4>Members may participate in any of our three annual sales.</h4>\r\n<h4>Shared kiln firings.</h4>\r\n<h4>Workshops, both internal skill shares and by skilled artists we bring in. <span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"> Some fees may apply.</span></h4>\r\n<h4>Helpful and experienced members who are willing to share what they know.</h4>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://localhost/membership/\">Learn More</a></h3>\r\n<div id=\"events\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-2189\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Events-226x300.png\" alt=\"Pottery Events Vancouver Island Icon\" width=\"256\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"http://localhost/events-2/\">View Upcoming Events</a></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"http://localhost/events-page/\">View Upcoming Sales</a></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Front Page', ''